item.title: Carson campaign funds skyrocket
item.description: Ben Carson's presidential campaign says it's close to having raised $20 million in the traditionally slow summer fundraising quarter, a figure that would be the largest announced haul of any Republican so far this cycle and give the insurgent new political durability.

item.title: Why is this on Clinton's private server?
